request.description:
Mendapatkan daftar semua pilihan Skill & SubSkill yang valid. Digunakan sebagai data dropdown di form Register/Edit Profil.

### Expected Response
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Skill options retrieved successfully",
  "data": {
    "skills": ["FRONTEND_DEVELOPMENT", "BACKEND_DEVELOPMENT", "DEVOPS_PLATFORM_ENGINEERING", "...dll"],
    "subSkills": ["REACT", "NODEJS", "DOCKER", "KUBERNETES", "...dll"]
  }
}
```

Memperbarui Access Token yang sudah kedaluwarsa menggunakan Refresh Token. Access Token baru otomatis tersimpan.

### Expected Response (200)
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Access token refreshed",
  "data": {
    "accessToken": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...(Token Baru)"
  }
}
```

### Error: Refresh Token tidak valid/kedaluwarsa (401)
```json
{
  "success": false,
  "message": "Invalid or expired refresh token"
}
```

Memperbarui data profil user (nama, password, skills, subSkills). Semua field bersifat opsional.

### Expected Response (200)
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Profile updated successfully",
  "data": {
    "user": {
      "id": "uuid",
      "name": "Nama Talent Updated",
      "email": "talent_baru@example.com",
      "role": "talent",
      "skills": ["FRONTEND_DEVELOPMENT", "BACKEND_DEVELOPMENT"],
      "subSkills": ["REACT", "NODEJS"],
      "isActive": true
    }
  }
}
```

Login sebagai Admin. Token Admin otomatis tersimpan ke `admin_access_token` dan `admin_refresh_token`.

### Expected Response (200)
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Login successful",
  "data": {
    "accessToken": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...",
    "refreshToken": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...",
    "user": {
      "id": "uuid",
      "name": "Admin Utama",
      "email": "admin@example.com",
      "role": "admin",
      "isActive": true
    }
  }
}
```

Mendapatkan data profil Admin yang sedang login.

### Expected Response (200)
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Profile retrieved successfully",
  "data": {
    "user": {
      "id": "uuid",
      "name": "Admin Utama",
      "email": "admin@example.com",
      "role": "admin",
      "isActive": true,
      "projectCompletions": []
    }
  }
}
```

Mendaftarkan user baru dengan role apapun (talent, client, atau admin). HANYA bisa diakses oleh Admin.

### Expected Response (200)
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "User registered successfully",
  "data": {
    "user": {
      "id": "uuid-baru",
      "name": "Admin Kedua",
      "email": "admin2@example.com",
      "role": "admin",
      "isActive": true
    }
  }
}
```

### Error: Bukan Admin (403)
```json
{
  "success": false,
  "message": "Forbidden: You do not have permission to access this resource"
}
```

Menonaktifkan akun user target. Setelah dinonaktifkan, user tidak bisa login lagi. HANYA bisa diakses oleh Admin.

**Catatan:** Variabel `{{talent_user_id}}` otomatis terisi dari hasil Register Talent di atas. Anda juga bisa menggantinya manual dengan UUID user lain.

### Expected Response (200)
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "User deactivated successfully",
  "data": {
    "user": {
      "id": "uuid-target",
      "name": "User Talent Baru",
      "email": "talent_baru@example.com",
      "role": "talent",
      "isActive": false
    }
  }
}
```

### Error: Admin tidak bisa mematikan dirinya sendiri (400)
```json
{
  "success": false,
  "message": "Cannot deactivate your own account"
}
```

### Error: User tidak ditemukan (404)
```json
{
  "success": false,
  "message": "User not found"
}
```

Mendapatkan semua data user. Digunakan oleh microservice lain (Bidding, Match, dll).

**Autentikasi:** Menggunakan `x-api-key` header, bukan Bearer Token.

### Expected Response (200)
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Users retrieved",
  "data": {
    "users": [
      {
        "id": "uuid",
        "name": "User Talent Baru",
        "email": "talent_baru@example.com",
        "role": "talent",
        "skills": ["FRONTEND_DEVELOPMENT"],
        "isActive": true
      }
    ],
    "total": 1
  }
}
```

### Error: API Key salah (401)
```json
{
  "success": false,
  "message": "Unauthorized: Invalid API key"
}
```

Mendapatkan data user berdasarkan UUID. Digunakan oleh microservice lain.

### Expected Response (200)
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "User found",
  "data": {
    "user": {
      "id": "uuid",
      "name": "User Talent Baru",
      "email": "talent_baru@example.com",
      "role": "talent",
      "skills": ["FRONTEND_DEVELOPMENT"],
      "isActive": true
    }
  }
}
```

### Error: User tidak ditemukan (404)
```json
{
  "success": false,
  "message": "User not found"
}
```

Memvalidasi JWT Access Token. Digunakan oleh microservice lain (Bidding, Match, dll) untuk memverifikasi identitas user.

### Expected Response (200)
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Token is valid",
  "data": {
    "user": {
      "id": "uuid",
      "name": "User Talent Baru",
      "email": "talent_baru@example.com",
      "role": "talent",
      "jti": "unique-jwt-id",
      "iat": 1700000000,
      "exp": 1700000900
    }
  }
}
```

### Error: Token tidak valid (401)
```json
{
  "success": false,
  "message": "Invalid or expired token"
}
```

Mendapatkan riwayat audit log semua aktivitas. Mendukung filter berdasarkan userId, action, dan limit.

### Expected Response (200)
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Audit logs retrieved",
  "data": {
    "logs": [
      {
        "id": "uuid",
        "action": "LOGIN_SUCCESS",
        "userId": "uuid-user",
        "ip": "103.x.x.x",
        "userAgent": "PostmanRuntime/7.x",
        "metadata": {},
        "createdAt": "2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z"
      },
      {
        "id": "uuid",
        "action": "REGISTER",
        "userId": "uuid-user",
        "ip": "103.x.x.x",
        "metadata": { "role": "talent" },
        "createdAt": "2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z"
      }
    ],
    "total": 2
  }
}
```

Mendapatkan semua riwayat proyek yang telah diselesaikan oleh Talent tertentu.

### Expected Response (200)
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Project completions retrieved",
  "data": {
    "completions": [
      {
        "id": "uuid",
        "talentId": "uuid-talent",
        "projectId": "PROJECT-001",
        "tokenId": "NFT-TOKEN-123",
        "ipfsUri": "ipfs://QmExampleHash123...",
        "completionDate": "2024-06-01T10:00:00.000Z"
      }
    ],
    "total": 1
  }
}
```

### Error: talentId bukan UUID valid (422)
```json
{
  "success": false,
  "message": "talentId must be a valid UUID"
}
```
